        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Multiple renal tumors;

          -  Recurrence of renal tumor;

          -  Intolerance to iodine-containing contrast agents;

          -  Pregnancy;

          -  Patients with Bosniak 4 cysts

          -  Presence of other oncological diseases;

